snippet.title: Fredbear and Friends: Left to Rot Trailer
snippet.description:
"Fredbear and Friends: Left to Rot" is an indie fan-game of Scott Cawthon's "Five Nights at Freddy's" and runs in the "Fredbear's Fright" storyline.

Follow the game on GameJolt! : https://gamejolt.com/games/fbafltr/298057
